    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着野村（Nomura）看到更多的削减速度，泰国机器人将重点转移到增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/thai-bot-shifts-focus-to-growth-as-nomura-sees-more-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国银行设定的小组成员将其专注力转移到了该国弱势增长前景上，野村控股公司（Nomura Holdings Inc.）预测了更具积极的降低利率来支持经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/thai-bot-shifts-focus-to-growth-as-nomura-sees-more-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 04:51:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
